reviewText: Pentrex does another great job with capturing Conrail in action along the Pittsburgh line. Audio, video and narration are well done and the movie is laid out and paced very well too. 5 stars.
Excellent DVD on the old Conrail Pittsburgh Line. Some of the places he mentions in the DVD I've been to!
Great condition! No scratches on the disc.
Nice tour thru the Puttsburgh railroad region during the Conrail days
